## Animation & Transitions

### Duration
- **fast:** 150ms (hover states, ripples)
- **DEFAULT:** 200ms (most UI transitions)
- **slow:** 300ms (modals, drawers, page transitions)

### Easing
- **DEFAULT:** ease-in-out
- **enter:** ease-out (appearing elements)
- **exit:** ease-in (disappearing elements)
- **bounce (optional):** cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.55, 0.265, 1.55)

### Common Patterns
- **Button hover:** `background-color 150ms ease-in-out`
- **Modal enter:** `opacity 200ms ease-out, scale 200ms ease-out`
- **Dropdown:** `opacity 150ms ease-out, translateY 150ms ease-out`
- **Fade in:** `opacity 200ms ease-out`
- **Slide up:** `transform 250ms ease-out, opacity 200ms ease-out`

