## Rules

1. **All components must use tokens defined here** - no hardcoded values
2. **Primary actions** use Accent (Orange/Coral)
3. **Secondary actions** use Secondary Accent (Muted Blue)
4. **Destructive actions** use Error (Red)
5. **Success feedback** uses Success (Green)
6. **Mobile-first** - design for 375px width minimum, scale up
7. **Touch-friendly** - minimum 44px tap targets on mobile
8. **Consistent spacing** - use Tailwind scale, no arbitrary values
9. **Icons from lucide-react only** - no mixing icon libraries
10. **Transitions** - add to all interactive elements (buttons, hover states)

