Every component/page must:
- [ ] Work on mobile (375px minimum width)
- [ ] Touch targets ≥ 44px on mobile
- [ ] Text readable without zooming
- [ ] Forms usable with mobile keyboard
- [ ] Navigation accessible (hamburger/drawer or bottom nav)
- [ ] Images scale appropriately (use next/image)
- [ ] No horizontal scroll (unless intentional)
- [ ] Loading states for slow connections
- [ ] Tested on real devices (iOS Safari, Android Chrome)
- [ ] WCAG 2.1 AA compliant (contrast, focus, keyboard)

